<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <title>Error Occurred</title>
</head>
<body>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 100px;
            color: #ff4f4f;
            margin: 0;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

    </style>



    <div class="container">
        <h1>Error</h1>
        <h2>Status Code: <%= statusCode %></h2>
        <p>Hmmm, That's Odd. Something Went Wrong. Please Try Turning Off Your ADBLOCKER Turn Off And Make Sure Your Xml File Is Valid. If You Believe It Is Valid Try Again Later Or Contact The Developer.</p>
        <p><strong>Error Message:</strong> <%= errorMessage %></p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Go to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
